[SN]TITLE[SN]
Magherafelt attack: Pensioner left shaken after petrol bombing

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A woman in her 70s has been left shaken by a petrol bomb attack on her home in Magherafelt, County Londonderry.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
1 January 2015 Last updated at 19:00 GMT
Two petrol bombs were thrown at her property on Wednesday night.
One of them ignited causing scorch damage to a window and door.  BBC Newsline's Helen Jones reports.
